---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | cssamurai" description="About cssamurai - politics, design, and technology blogger">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mb-12">
      <p>
        Hello, I'm the voice behind cssamurai. This blog represents my ongoing exploration of politics, design, and technology—three domains that increasingly shape our experience of the world.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        My background spans political science and digital design, giving me a unique perspective on how these fields intersect and influence one another. I believe that understanding these connections is crucial for navigating our complex digital landscape.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What I Write About</h2>
      
      <h3>Politics</h3>
      <p>
        I analyze current political movements, policy decisions, and their implications for society. My approach is analytical rather than partisan, focusing on understanding underlying structures and trends.
      </p>
      
      <h3>Design</h3>
      <p>
        From UI/UX principles to broader questions about design ethics, I explore how visual and experiential choices shape our interactions with technology and information. I'm particularly interested in how design can either reinforce or challenge existing power dynamics.
      </p>
      
      <h3>Technology</h3>
      <p>
        I cover emerging technologies, digital platforms, and their social implications. Rather than pure technical analysis, I focus on how technology transforms our communication, civic engagement, and daily experiences.
      </p>
      
      <h2>My Approach</h2>
      <p>
        My writing aims to be:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Thoughtful</strong> — Providing nuanced analysis rather than hot takes</li>
        <li><strong>Accessible</strong> — Making complex topics understandable without oversimplification</li>
        <li><strong>Interdisciplinary</strong> — Drawing connections across traditional boundaries</li>
        <li><strong>Ethical</strong> — Considering the moral dimensions of design and technology choices</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <p>
        I value dialogue and diverse perspectives. Feel free to reach out via social media or email to continue the conversation.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
      <a 
        href="/blog" 
        class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-5 py-3 bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 text-white font-medium rounded-md transition-colors"
      >
        Read the Blog
      </a>
      <a 
        href="mailto:hello@cssamurai.com" 
        class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-5 py-3 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-800 hover:bg-primary-200 dark:hover:bg-primary-700 text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 font-medium rounded-md transition-colors"
      >
        Contact Me
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>